There is not enough control over deleting spaces. 

Administrators by default, are given "Admin" rights to all Spaces. However, this should be redefined to include "Delete Space" permissions as a separate option to provide more control. 

It would be useful to include "Delete" under the "Space" Permissions group when modifying the permissions of a given Space. This way, it can prevent "human error" caused by space admins.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *Confluence Server*. Using *Confluence Cloud*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONFCLOUD-8059].
