The getChildren remote API function should return a list of all the top level pages if passed 0 for pageId.

I want to use the Remote API to walk the page hierarchy.  The space is very large (over 10,000 pages), so I do not want to use the getPages function for a list of all the pages.  I would like to be able to use the getChildren function to get a list of all the top level pages, and then work my way down.  However, it returns an error:  You're not allowed to view that page, or it does not exist.

