Sometimes you really want to see the date / time a pgae was created and edited. At the moment you have to use th "Info" tab to achieve this. Putting this info on the page all the time would probably clutter it but if you add the exact date / times as a tooltip of on "Added By" and "Update by" then that gives you access (not great access mind you) to these dates without the clutter
